{"id":233006112,"title":"鬼點子計畫—7","content":"好久不見啊啊啊啊\n過年忙著煮年夜菜+開市一直沒有時間可以發文\n也剛好遇上了點子荒\n不過！最近又想到一到有趣的簡單料理\n松露蕈菇炒飯\n這道菜是改變自義大利的燉飯\n飯粒粒分明充滿松露及蕈菇的香氣\n那下面就來為各位介紹\n------------------------------\n分量-1人份\n時間-15分鐘\n\n飯-1碗（食量大2碗）\n蘑菇-10顆切片\n杏鮑菇-1根切碎\n奶油-20克\n橄欖油-3餐匙\n莫札瑞拉起司-100克\n松露鹽-適量\n\n-------------作法--------------\n1.先將鍋子燒熱後加入橄欖油，下蘑菇炒至水分蒸發\n2.下杏鮑菇炒至有蕈菇香味\n3.將飯加下去拌炒（切記不可用炒勺將飯切碎）\n4.加入奶油、起司並調味後快速翻鍋/拌勻\n5.擺盤後灑上少許松露鹽即可\n\n\n\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9f718eb7-ef7e-47c8-a838-3083c2a22657/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"好久不見啊啊啊啊，過年忙著煮年夜菜+開市一直沒有時間可以發文，也剛好遇上了點子荒，不過！最近又想到一到有趣的簡單料理，松露蕈菇炒飯，這道菜是改變自義大利的燉飯，飯粒粒分明充滿松露及蕈菇的香氣，那下面就","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T04:34:28.029Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T04:34:28.029Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":["點子","烹飪","食譜","在家輕鬆做","美食"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"國立高雄餐旅大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":8}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9f718eb7-ef7e-47c8-a838-3083c2a22657/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"fd23d141-fc77-47fa-a373-51dda779b5a4","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9f718eb7-ef7e-47c8-a838-3083c2a22657/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9f718eb7-ef7e-47c8-a838-3083c2a22657/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9f718eb7-ef7e-47c8-a838-3083c2a22657/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T04:34:28.029Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T04:34:28.029Z","width":480,"height":640},{"id":"fd23d141-fc77-47fa-a373-51dda779b5a4","ur